{"tid":1763070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"tommy事件引申一樣嘢，我地要接受黃絲唔係聖人，都會犯錯同失德，反而我地要思考點面對呢啲會不斷發生嘅事情","createTime":"2019-11-30T04:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T03:48:02.000Z","uid":31215,"like":150,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d16374ecae501bc0c35241eddb5ad6e1e9dd55","tid":1763070,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"Tommy應該係第一個被追擊嘅同路人<br />\n土共最鍾意見到呢啲<br />\n我敢肯定土共一定派人推波助瀾<br />\n推到佢冇得翻身<br />\n然後少一個高調公開反共嘅人<br />\n<br />\n但我地要認清楚一件事<br />\n黃絲從來唔係聖人<br />\n我地都可能有私心嘅時候、會犯錯、會有抵受唔住誘惑、做錯決定嘅時候<br />\n加上尋日細良都指出<br />\n土共會不斷試探同路人<br />\n引佢地犯錯<br />\n同時會誇大矛盾<br />\n逐個打擊<br />\n我地要接受呢幾年會越嚟越多手足會俾人捉到錯處、醜聞<br />\n今次係tommy<br />\n下一個係任何一個我地愛戴嘅人<br />\n<br />\n咁我地應該用咩心態去做呢啲事情呢<br />\n有冇需要割蓆<br />\n然後打到佢永不翻身<br />\n定如果當時人肯道歉同檢討，我地就可以既往不究？<br />\n如果對方百屌唔成材，係咪低調處理算？好似藍絲同建制處理豬隊友咁咁，唔使日日提同打到對方永不超生？"},{"pid":"5bc3dff651f6c963fe18fa83400a3dd1a2541eda","tid":1763070,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"70eae90a3ebd35c633a3f2a4b5d6583f390dca12","tid":1763070,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774ac6576062e0cd12c75e4628cf59a18c3d156b","tid":1763070,"uid":261445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:54:00.000Z","msg":"借問一下咩事？"},{"pid":"3340f81a8728f7d3f2beb017f207312b7bc5d9d3","tid":1763070,"uid":155012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:55:28.000Z","msg":"跟本呢個圈既人都應該平等"},{"pid":"ce7be476f9dea4ed478443d6698d5ce093b76304","tid":1763070,"uid":31215,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"774ac6576062e0cd12c75e4628cf59a18c3d156b","tid":1763070,"uid":261445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:54:00.000Z","msg":"借問一下咩事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"Tommy做錯一件事<br />\n就係攻擊前輩<br />\n然後俾人群起挖以前嘅衰野<br />\n人格謀殺<br />\n將佢所有支持運動行為貶成博上為<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得佢有責任<br />\n但都有有心人助燃<br />\n<br />\nTommy之後肯定有其他同路人再中一樣嘅方式<br />\n<br />\n犯錯/搵到醜聞-&gt;攻擊+有心人助燃-&gt;打擊成功"},{"pid":"8062be72b7b7b1d6419fc70b5977bcb28ebf46ce","tid":1763070,"uid":1654,"like":7,"dislike":11,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"唔覺得tommy 有錯"},{"pid":"0eb5bd2fba6dfb63c84d622552b0780c52639174","tid":1763070,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3340f81a8728f7d3f2beb017f207312b7bc5d9d3","tid":1763070,"uid":155012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:55:28.000Z","msg":"跟本呢個圈既人都應該平等"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"同社會一樣<br />\n要諗懲罰與包容原諒之間點作出取捨同平衡"},{"pid":"fb78198a44865fc0ad686f4c782811515ed28860","tid":1763070,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d035c7610e1a77ac6ec71a846162b44fe11bef0","tid":1763070,"uid":31215,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"8062be72b7b7b1d6419fc70b5977bcb28ebf46ce","tid":1763070,"uid":1654,"like":7,"dislike":11,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"唔覺得tommy 有錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:03:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得話前輩做多左<br />\n但拎以前嘅野黎否定而家嘅所作所為都做多左"},{"pid":"cc1ec812577b2c56ffdf652cfe63d6a8ebcadf0a","tid":1763070,"uid":193233,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"香港人道德標準真係好高！"},{"pid":"b258f656344826b0d9835f2ea2cbdf3048719e35","tid":1763070,"uid":123168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:04:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91fd49b7fe859990dc94c944b858708ae19c5283","tid":1763070,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/